  </Content>
  <!-- Steps2 Widget ****************** -->

  <Steps2
    title="Our vision"
    subtitle=`"I take this very seriously. Too many kids these days are forced into learning programming, especially competitive programming. So they learn, because they were forced to learn. But then afterwards, they realize that their skills are put to waste as they did not know how to put them into practical use. I want to change that with this club."<br/><br/> - Bryan Hu, Co-President`
    items={[
      {
        title: "To <b>empower</b> students",
        description:
          "I want our club to bring the very best out of people, allowing them to build great things without anything to slow them down.",
      },
      {
        title: "To <b>impact</b> others",
        description:
          "I want to be able to create a tangible impact on the world what we do (in a positive way), which includes reaching out to the local community",
      },
      {
        title: "To be <b>sustainable</b>",
        description:
          "I don't want this club to just die out when I graduate but instead, I want it to be a club that lasts for a long time. A long enough time that it can create a real impact on the next generation of software engineers",
      },
    ]}
  />

